00:01:06.599 --> 00:01:08.599
to discuss with the officials.

00:01:28.560 --> 00:01:29.079
Awesome!

00:01:30.079 --> 00:01:32.480
We've now reclaimed
partial military control.

00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:35.519
However, Gao Ji has
controlled the court for long.

00:01:35.920 --> 00:01:37.079
It will take much longer

00:01:37.640 --> 00:01:38.519
to topple him.

00:01:40.640 --> 00:01:42.680
More court officials support you now.

00:01:43.040 --> 00:01:45.159
Gao Ji dares not act recklessly.

00:01:45.879 --> 00:01:46.959
He can't deploy troops now,

00:01:47.480 --> 00:01:48.480
and his power is waning.

00:01:49.239 --> 00:01:51.079
We should proceed with careful strategy.

00:02:02.439 --> 00:02:02.840
Nan,

00:02:04.400 --> 00:02:05.560
after we regain power,

00:02:06.079 --> 00:02:06.680
