00:02:18.879 --> 00:02:20.199
I've thought it through.

00:02:20.879 --> 00:02:22.360
Maybe it all started because of me.

00:02:23.319 --> 00:02:24.319
The Pingxiang rebellion,

00:02:24.560 --> 00:02:25.520
and Gao Ji's betrayal...

00:02:28.080 --> 00:02:29.159
