00:03:23.319 --> 00:03:24.639
and is more decisive than I am.

00:03:25.199 --> 00:03:25.759
I know

00:03:26.680 --> 00:03:28.280
you're still guilty of that shot

00:03:28.280 --> 00:03:29.039
ten years ago.

00:03:30.199 --> 00:03:31.199
But I think

00:03:32.240 --> 00:03:33.199
he no longer

00:03:33.439 --> 00:03:35.439
desires the throne anymore.

00:03:37.039 --> 00:03:37.520
Why?

00:03:38.360 --> 00:03:39.560
You're biological brothers,

00:03:40.199 --> 00:03:42.439
but I was raised under his guidance.

00:03:42.680 --> 00:03:43.560
I know him better.

00:04:00.704 --> 00:04:01.479
Oh, no.

00:04:04.080 --> 00:04:04.840
Lock him up.

00:04:05.199 --> 00:04:05.728
Yes!

00:04:13.159 --> 00:04:13.879
Don't...

00:04:13.879 --> 00:04:15.520
