00:04:25.120 --> 00:04:25.839
All these years,

00:04:25.839 --> 00:04:27.319
I've been lurking around Shi Nan

00:04:27.560 --> 00:04:28.680
and addressed him as Master,

00:04:28.920 --> 00:04:31.240
solely to capture this rebel

00:04:31.680 --> 00:04:33.120
and take him to the Prince Regent.

00:04:34.800 --> 00:04:36.040
Then tell me.

00:04:36.399 --> 00:04:39.240
Did you abduct Her Grace?

00:04:41.000 --> 00:04:41.720
No!

00:04:42.160 --> 00:04:43.360
Shi Nan ordered everything.

00:04:43.639 --> 00:04:45.360
It has nothing to do with me.

00:04:45.759 --> 00:04:47.560
Yet you carried out the capture.

00:04:49.480 --> 00:04:50.879
Sir, please spare me.

00:04:51.079 --> 00:04:51.639
I...

00:04:52.399 --> 00:04:53.600
I am truly useful to you.

00:04:54.000 --> 00:04:55.439
I am truly useful to you.

