00:05:40.600 --> 00:05:41.759
Who is he really?

00:05:43.439 --> 00:05:44.439
Who is he?

00:05:45.879 --> 00:05:46.839
Well,

00:05:47.160 --> 00:05:49.759
he should call you brother.

00:06:02.199 --> 00:06:03.600
You want me to kill him so much?

00:06:08.600 --> 00:06:09.696
Does he know

00:06:09.696 --> 00:06:11.319
some grave secret of yours?

00:06:18.720 --> 00:06:20.224
What a moonlit,

00:06:20.639 --> 00:06:22.240
star-sparse night.

00:06:22.639 --> 00:06:23.240
You two,

00:06:24.000 --> 00:06:25.000
